headline: Revisiting Stock Picks Berkshire Hathaway, Deere, Vita Coco. What the Charts Say.
summary: Taking time to revisit former stock picks can be just as valuable as identifying new opportunities.  Technology is a cellar dweller this year, ranking 10th of 11 major  sectors, ahead of only financials.  In contrast, industrials and consumer staples both sit in the top four and account for two thirds of today’s ideas.
